main event: A civilian reported a UFO sighting in Wooddale, Illinois on August 23, 1965.
interesting points: The object was described as initially appearing as two blinking lights that transformed into three blinking white lights,The witness observed a loud motor sound, not typical of any jet or helicopter,The lights were stationary and estimated to be 2-3 telephone poles in height,The object disappeared to the NNE after 7 minutes of observation,The observation was made from inside a house through a front window.
sighted object: one silver metallic disc with blinking lights
witness description: James Crawford, 28 years old, laborer, good reliability
